                "Unified view of RevPAR, occupancy, ADR, EBITDA margin, loyalty engagement, and booking channel mix across regions and segments. The September anomaly should visibly stand out in daily operational lines while monthly P&L counters frame the financial impact. Root-cause table ties delayed conversions and ESG spikes to the margin contraction.\n"
